imdb.plot outline: WHAT'S YOUR DREAM? Fan favorite of Bravo's Make Me A Supermodel, Ronnie Kroell, joins forces with Hollywood funny man "Laughing" Eddie Lobo, to navigate the challenges of bringing dreams to life. With 20 years between them and both recently single, watch them juggling auditions, preparing for the red carpet, and operating the day to day business of their company - Friend Movement. With each new episode, follow this dynamic duo as they leverage their expansive network of industry professionals to bring your dreams to life.
